          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "All of the fission yields must, however, be expressed",
                "as upper limits for the following reasons: (a) no",
                "firm evidence for 42Ar or for 56 Co was found; the",
                "method of analyses used merely assumed that some was",
                "present, and (b) 37Ar, 39Ar, and 41Ar could have been",
                "formed by reactions of neutrons with trace impurities",
                "in the sample, such as (n,gamma) reactions with argon,",
                " (n,p) reactions with potassium, and (n,alpha)",
                "reactions with calcium. A reasonable upper limit to",
                "assign each yield is the sum of the calculated yield",
                "and its standard deviation."
              ]
            }
          ],
